snippet.title: CARACOLES "The Fastest Slow Racing Game Ever"
snippet.description:
Hilarious like a fart... but longer! In Caracoles you compete in the fastest outrageously slow racing multiplayer battles ever. Free Demo available on Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/2412180/Caracoles/

Also available on
AppStore https://apps.apple.com/us/app/caracoles/id1598913652
PlayStore https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Yonder.Caracoles

Join our Discord for new updates: https://discord.gg/5hwrRQjAvW

Credits: Music by Dokaka
